Package: dyntftpd
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, adduser, python-daemon (>= 0.1.1-1),
 python-tftpy (>= 0.4.5-1~fsmi6)
Description: TFTP daemon with support for dynamic generation of content
 This tftp daemon provides hooks to generate content on the fly using
 user-provided Python code or a set of built-in modes.
 .
 Currently the following overlay types are provided:
   * deliver the newest Linux kernel image from a set of images,
   * generate pxelinux configuration files based on per-client settings (i.e.
     user provided Python code) and
   * take static file from regular file system.
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
